    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401090/extras/fcde8ed7ffa4037b5783955e06e88e22.webp?t=1722871263\" width=617 height=57 /></span><br><br>Welcome to the Cleanup Crew. <br><br>Take control of one of our resourceful agents, ready to go on dangerous missions without them knowing that they are actually disposable clones (convenient right?). <br><br>Scavenge anything of value, exterminate all in sight, and gather precious genetic material.<br><br>Infinite realities, apocalyptic planets, mindless zombie fairy tales hordes, AI-controlled robots, are all common everyday occurrences here. <br><br>Help the agents survive long enough to make profitable extractions, improve the team and your arsenal and get ready to go again! and again! AND AGAIN!<br><br><br><strong>CHOOSE</strong> your loadout from a pool of Clone Agents and Main Guns.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401090/extras/2e87edb2165095cf20e4dcd5e0896bed.poster.avif?t=1722871263\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401090/extras/2e87edb2165095cf20e4dcd5e0896bed.webm?t=1722871263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401090/extras/2e87edb2165095cf20e4dcd5e0896bed.mp4?t=1722871263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CUSTOMIZE</strong> your build, choose from several Sub Weapons and Perks<br><strong>ACCOMPLISH</strong> emergent objectives that put your strategy and quick reactions to the test<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2401090/extras/e2e6b1c43890aea63fc8cf1a59cf8f48.poster.avif?t=17228